Sentencas: We have studied the structure and electrical properties of La2Mo2O9 thin films of different thicknesses prepared by the laser deposition technique at different substrate temperatures.
Titulo: Structural and electrical transport properties of La2Mo2O9 thin films prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: The structural properties of the thin films have been investigated using XRD, XPS, AFM, TEM, SEM, and Raman spectroscopy.
Titulo: Structural and electrical transport properties of La2Mo2O9 thin films prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: The electrical transport properties of the thin films have been investigated in wide temperature and frequency ranges.
Titulo: Structural and electrical transport properties of La2Mo2O9 thin films prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: The cubic nature of the thin films has been confirmed from structural analysis.
Titulo: Structural and electrical transport properties of La2Mo2O9 thin films prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: An enhancement of the oxygen ion conductivity of the films up to five orders of magnitude is obtained compared to that of the bulk La2Mo2O9, suggesting usefulness of the thin films as electrolytes in micro-solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Structural and electrical transport properties of La2Mo2O9 thin films prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: The enhanced dc ionic conductivity of the thin films has been interpreted using the rule of the mixture model, while a power law model has been used to investigate the frequency and temperature dependences of the conductivity.
Titulo: Structural and electrical transport properties of La2Mo2O9 thin films prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: The analysis of the results predicts the three-dimensional oxygen ion conduction in the thin films.
Titulo: Structural and electrical transport properties of La2Mo2O9 thin films prepared by pulsed laser deposition
